title: SFMW 802-808mp3+cdg format Karaoke
description:
Seeing as how I have had a fair few files of here its time for me to give back something to all you nice people, now its my first time uploading here so i hope this works ok for you all.

This is Sunfly Most Wanted number 802-808, all files are in the MP3 and CDG format, I know some of you use the zip style so if anyone wants to reup it in that format then please feel free to do so.

If this first torrent works out ok i will upload the rest of my collection over the next few weeks/months, I have about 7000 files to share.

I already have the next 7 (809-815) ready to up if this works out ok.
